      • read

        public void read​(java.nio.channels.SelectionKey key)
          throws java.io.IOException
        Method to process the command from the client. Each command has a unique key. 1 - information about a client 2 - file uploading 3 - message sending 4 - file downloading 5 - exit 6 - getting information about clients
        Parameters:
        key - client key
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - thrown if something went wrong during getting information from client
